alic;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left}</style></head><body class="c3"><p class="c0"><span class="c4">S&#7913;c m&#7841;nh kh&ocirc;ng d&#7877; b&#7883; chia r&#7869;</span></p><p class="c0 c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">C&oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7853;p website, vi&#7871;t blog v&#7873; c&aacute;c v&#7845;n n&#7841;n t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam&hellip;</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">C&oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i mi&#7879;t m&agrave;i vi&#7871;t v&#7873; c&aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7873; khai ph&oacute;ng, c&aacute;c gi&aacute; tr&#7883; c&#7911;a quy&#7873;n t&#7921; do&hellip;</span></p><p class="c0 c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">B&#7903;i l&#7869;, c&ograve;n r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i Vi&#7879;t c&ograve;n quan t&acirc;m &#273;&#7871;n v&#7853;n m&#7879;nh c&#7911;a &#273;&#7845;t n&#432;&#7899;c, &#273;&#7873;u m&#417; m&#7897;t &#432;&#7899;c mu&#7889;ng v&#7873; t&#432;&#417;ng lai m&#7897;t Vi&#7879;t Nam t&#432;&#417;i &#273;&#7865;p h&#417;n, X&atilde; H&#7897;i nh&acirc;n b&#7843;n h&#417;n, Qu&#7889;c Gia h&ugrave;ng m&#7841;nh h&#417;n&hellip;</span></p><p class="c0 c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">L&agrave; d&acirc;n k&#7929; thu&#7853;t, t&ocirc;i nh&igrave;n th&#7845;y nhi&#7873;u c&#417; h&#7897;i &#273;&#7875; m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i c&ugrave;ng chung tay g&#7855;n k&#7871;t l&#7841;i v&#7899;i nhau, c&ugrave;ng bi&#7871;n gi&#7845;c m&#417; Vi&#7879;t Nam gi&agrave;u m&#7841;nh, nh&acirc;n b&#7843;n th&agrave;nh hi&#7879;n th&#7921;c.</span></p><p class="c0 c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Cu&#7897;c c&aacute;ch m&#7841;ng Internet &#273;&atilde; v&agrave; &#273;ang l&agrave;m thay &#273;&#7893;i x&atilde; h&#7897;i to&agrave;n c&#7847;u. Ch&#7845;n &#273;&#7897;ng m&#7841;nh nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a Internet l&agrave; &#7903; hai l&#297;nh v&#7921;c truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng v&agrave; mua b&aacute;n l&#7867; (media, retail). Trong ngh&agrave;nh truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng, b&aacute;o gi&#7845;y &#273;&atilde; b&#7883; thay th&#7871; b&#7857;ng tin t&#7913;c tr&ecirc;n nh&#7919;ng trang m&#7841;ng &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917;. &#272;&#7897;i ng&#361; bi&ecirc;n t&#7853;p, ph&oacute;ng vi&ecirc;n chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p b&#7883; thay b&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i th&ocirc;ng minh. Ngh&agrave;nh bu&ocirc;n b&aacute;n l&#7867; truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng c&#361;ng d&#7847;n b&#7883; khai t&#7917;, thay v&agrave;o &#273;&oacute; l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng gian h&agrave;ng tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n v&#7899;i v&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; khi&ecirc;m t&#7889;n nh&#432;ng hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; t&#7915; s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng to&agrave;n c&#7847;u.</span></p><p class="c0 c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">C&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng c&oacute; s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh t&#7915;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c coi nh&#432; l&agrave; quy&#7873;n l&#7921;c nh&aacute;nh th&#7913; t&#432; c&#7911;a ch&iacute;nh quy&#7873;n n&#432;&#7899;c M&#7929; c&#361;ng &#273;ang b&#7883; th&#7845;t th&#7871; trong th&#7901;i &#273;&#7841;i Internet. M&#7897;t c&ocirc;ng ty truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng m&#7899;i kh&ocirc;ng t&ecirc;n tu&#7893;i l&agrave; Breitbart Network &#273;&atilde; &#273;&oacute;ng vai tr&ograve; kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7887; trong vi&#7879;c v&#7853;n &#273;&#7897;ng c&#7917; tri b&#7887; phi&#7871;u cho &#273;&#7843;ng CH, gi&aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c c&#7911;a c&ocirc;ng ty &#7845;y &#273;ang l&agrave; c&#7889; v&#7845;n th&acirc;n c&#7853;n c&#7911;a TT Trump.</span></p><p class="c0 c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Facebook l&agrave; m&#7897;t minh ch&#7913;ng cho s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng c&#7911;a c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng m&#7841;ng. Facebook k&#7871;t n&#7889;i m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7841;i v&#7899;i nhau t&#7841;o n&ecirc;n m&#7897;t qu&#7847;n th&#7875; s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh trong v&ocirc; h&igrave;nh. Nh&#7901; c&oacute; Facebook m&agrave; c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;&#7845;u tranh &#273;&ograve;i d&acirc;n ch&#7911; cho Vi&#7879;t Nam trong c&#361;ng nh&#432; ngo&agrave;i n&#432;&#7899;c kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n &#273;&#417;n &#273;&#7897;c nh&#432; tr&#432;&#7899;c n&#7919;a. C&#361;ng nh&#7901; c&oacute; facebook m&agrave; c&aacute;c v&#7909; &#273;&agrave;n &aacute;p, b&#7855;t b&#7899; v&agrave; tham quan h&#7889;i l&#7897; d&#7847;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a ra &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng.</span></p><p class="c0 c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Ng&agrave;y nay &#7903; M&#7929;, c&aacute;c t&#7853;p &#273;o&agrave;n bu&ocirc;n b&aacute;n nh&#7887; l&#7867; &#273;ang g&#7863;p kh&oacute; kh&#259;n c&#7841;nh tranh v&#7899;i c&aacute;c c&#7917;a h&agrave;ng th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n. Nhi&#7873;u t&#7853;p &#273;o&agrave;n l&acirc;u &#273;&#7901;i nay g&#7863;p nguy c&#417; ph&aacute; s&#7843;n v&agrave; ph&#7843;i &#273;&oacute;ng c&#7917;a nhi&#7873;u ti&#7879;m. Th&#432;&#417;ng x&aacute; (mall) m&#7897;t th&#7901;i l&agrave; ch&#7889;n sinh ho&#7841;t c&#7911;a thanh ni&ecirc;n m&#7899;i l&#7899;n nay ch&#7881; c&ograve;n l&agrave; khung s&#432;&#7901;n c&#7911;a d&#297; v&atilde;ng ho&agrave;nh tr&aacute;ng. Th&#7871; nh&#432;ng n&#432;&#7899;c M&#7929; l&agrave; n&#417;i c&#7911;a s&#7921; ph&aacute; ho&#7841;i s&aacute;ng t&#7841;o (creative destruction). Nhi&#7873;u k&#7929; thu&#7853;t c&#361; k&#7929; b&#7883; d&#7865;p b&#7887; m&#7903; ra c&#417; h&#7897;i cho m&#7897;t n&#7873;n tr&#7853;t t&#7921; m&#7899;i.</span></p><p class="c0 c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Nh&#432; v&#7853;y kh&#7889;i c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i Vi&#7879;t c&oacute; l&#7907;i th&#7871; g&igrave; trong b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh c&#7911;a n&#7873;n tr&#7853;t t&#7921; m&#7899;i trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c bu&ocirc;n b&aacute;n l&#7867; v&agrave; truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng?</span></p><p class="c0 c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">&ldquo;&#272;&ocirc;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7853;p th&agrave;nh ch&#7907;&quot;, &#273;&oacute; l&agrave; g&#7889;c r&#7877; c&#7911;a n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; Vi&#7879;t Nam t&#7915; x&#432;a &#273;&#7871;n nay. Tuy r&#7857;ng s&#7889; ng&#432;&#7901;i Vi&#7879;t online v&agrave; bi&#7871;t s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&#7841;ng internet r&#7845;t &#273;&ocirc;ng nh&#432;ng nhi&#7873;u r&agrave;o c&#7843;n kh&oacute; v&#432;&#7907;t qua &#273;&atilde; ng&#259;n c&#7843;n s&#7921; h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh c&#7911;a c&aacute;c ch&#7907; t&#7921; ph&aacute;t trong c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i Vi&#7879;t. Gi&#7843; s&#7917; m&#7885;i r&agrave;o c&#7843;n kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n n&#7919;a, ng&#432;&#7901;i Vi&#7879;t b&#7845;t lu&#7853;n trong hay ngo&agrave;i n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7873;u c&oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng bu&ocirc;n b&aacute;n v&#7899;i nhau, khi &#7845;y c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh kinh t&#7871; &#273;&#7911; s&#7913;c bi&#7871;n gi&#7845;c m&#417; chung Vi&#7879;t Nam tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh hi&#7879;n th&#7921;c.</span></p><p class="c0 c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Quay v&#7873; v&#7899;i th&#7921;c t&#7871; hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, mu&#7889;n l&#7853;p ch&#7907; ph&#7843;i c&oacute; &#273;&#7911; 4 y&#7871;u t&#7889; c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t: c&oacute; h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7875; b&aacute;n, c&oacute; c&aacute;ch giao h&agrave;ng cho kh&aacute;ch, c&oacute; ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n thanh kho&#7843;n, v&agrave; c&oacute; &#273;&aacute;m &#273;&ocirc;ng &#273;&#7875; l&#7853;p ch&#7907;. T&ocirc;i s&#7869; c&#7889; g&#7855;ng t&oacute;m l&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7919;ng y&#7871;u t&#7889; &#273;&oacute; trong b&agrave;i n&agrave;y &#273;&#7875; c&aacute;c b&#7841;n th&#7845;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh c&#7911;a m&#7895;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&uacute;ng ta.</span></p><p class="c0 c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">H&agrave;ng ho&aacute; &#273;&#7875; b&aacute;n kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; g&oacute;n g&#7885;n v&agrave;o nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; trong n&#432;&#7899;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, h&#7843;i ngo&#7841;i c&#7847;n v&agrave; ng&#432;&#7907;c l&#7841;i. M&#7897;t kh&aacute;i ni&#7879;m m&#7899;i cho ph&eacute;p m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i b&#7845;t k&#7875; &#7903; &#273;&acirc;u c&oacute; th&#7875; b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng b&#7845;t c&#7913; n&#417;i n&agrave;o m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, c&#7845;t gi&#7919; kho b&atilde;i, h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i c&#7911;a kh&aacute;i ni&#7879;m n&agrave;y ti&#7871;ng Anh g&#7885;i l&agrave; dropshipping. &nbsp;&#7902; c&aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c gi&agrave;u, gi&aacute; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&#7911;a m&#7897;t s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&#7881; l&agrave; ph&#7847;n tr&#259;m nh&#7887; so v&#7899;i gi&aacute; th&agrave;nh m&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng ph&#7843;i tr&#7843;. Ph&#7847;n l&#7899;n gi&aacute; c&#7843; &#273;&#7897;i l&ecirc;n cao l&agrave; do chi ph&iacute; cho qu&#7843;ng c&aacute;o, ti&#7871;p th&#7883;, v&agrave; &#273;&#7859;ng c&#7845;p th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u. V&iacute; d&#7909; m&#7897;t s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&ugrave;ng nh&agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t n&#7871;u &#273;&oacute;ng th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng nh&#432; Taylorswift s&#7869; &#273;&#7855;t ti&#7873;n g&#7845;p b&#7897;i h&#417;n nh&#7919;ng th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u kh&aacute;c. T&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; nh&#432; c&aacute;c t&#7901; b&aacute;o l&#7899;n b&#7883; Internet l&agrave;m lao &#273;ao tr&#432;&#7899;c c&aacute;c b&aacute;o m&#7841;ng kh&ocirc;ng t&ecirc;n tu&#7893;i ho&#7863;c l&agrave;m lu m&#7901; tr&#432;&#7899;c c&aa